              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2019-08-28T15:06:56.000+01:00">28 August 2019</time>
              After Brexit, if you import merchandise in baggage through any port or airport with a red channel or red phone point, you'll now be able to declare your goods and pay duty using an online service, as long as the goods are: below £900; weighing less than 1,000kg; not licensed or controlled; not excise goods. The guidance has been updated to reflect this.
            </li>
